{"tid":998714,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"漫畫《後街女孩》改編真人電視劇：三大特攝女主齊聚我的快樂源泉","createTime":"2019-01-28T07:15:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-09T00:57:37.000Z","uid":49391,"like":28,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"aaae7bba6e63375a0368417b2bccbb15cec0c420","tid":998714,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T07:15:56.000Z","msg":"Jasmine Gyuh在《周刊Young Magazine》上連載的搞笑漫畫《後街女孩》在動畫化、電影化之後又再次宣布改編真人版電視劇，全6集，另有加入原創角色：小宮有紗。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gm1Py1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgm1Py1e.jpg&h=a95e5842&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這部電視劇預計在2月17日開播和影版一樣，三名黑道組織成員由白洲迅、柾木玲彌、花沢將人出演，女偶像由岡本夏美、松田るか、坂ノ上茜出演，另外共演包括小宮有紗、小沢仁志、中野英雄、大杉漣（友情出演）、岩城滉一等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vNn7kGf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvNn7kGf.jpg&h=453a08cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f66LRNV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff66LRNV.jpg&h=99832ed8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n　講述混混三人組因做錯事被組長送到泰國被迫接受變性和整形手術、成為偶像組合出道替組長賺錢的故事、電視劇版比電影版更接近原作的篇章構成、將於2月17日開播​​​​<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5jExwNW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5jExwNW.jpg&h=ff60ed84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R4DVuzC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR4DVuzC.jpg&h=258a6520&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5xDRNmi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5xDRNmi.jpg&h=6b7033f2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8ff49e774fa588289de5da64788424d8c00515a3","tid":998714,"uid":49391,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T07:30:29.000Z","msg":"除左美利堅帝國之外,呢度仲有無巴打想變做絲打?<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d833157adf16392168e8946841d1a02c54aae079","tid":998714,"uid